Name: Bob
Message: Hello! How can I help you understand climate change better?

Name: Bob
Message: Sea levels are rising mainly due to thermal expansion (water expands as it warms) and melting ice from glaciers and ice sheets. This can lead to increased coastal flooding and erosion.

Name: tom HUMAN_____^^^
Message: hello guys, how can we control sea level rising?

Name: Bob
Message: We can help control rising sea levels by reducing greenhouse gas emissions, using renewable energy, conserving energy, and protecting natural carbon sinks like forests and wetlands. These actions help to limit global warming and ice melt.
